textfsm_template:
Value SEQ (\d+)
Value TTL (\d+)
Value TIME ([\d.]+)
Value PACKETS (\d+)
Value RECEIVED (\d+)
Value LOSS (\d+)
Value RT_MIN ([\d.]+)
Value RT_AVG ([\d.]+)
Value RT_MAX ([\d.]+)
Value RT_MDEV ([\d.]+)

Start
  ^\d+\s+bytes\s+from\s+\S+:\s+icmp_seq=${SEQ}\s+ttl=${TTL}\s+time=${TIME}\s+ms -> Record
  ^---\s+\S+\s+ping\s+statistics\s+---
  ^${PACKETS}\s+packets\s+transmitted,\s+${RECEIVED}\s+received,\s+${LOSS}%\s+packet\s+loss
  ^rtt\s+min/avg/max/mdev\s+=\s+${RT_MIN}/${RT_AVG}/${RT_MAX}/${RT_MDEV}\s+ms
